    <item>
      <title>[Counter-Strike] 个人设置j</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/counter-strike/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/counter-strike/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[Counter-Strike] 个人设置j</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="autoexeccfg">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#autoexeccfg"></a>
autoexec.cfg
</h2><blockquote>
<p>D:\SteamLibrary\steamapps\common\Counter-Strike Global Offensive\game\csgo\cfg\autoexec.cfg</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><code>binddefaults</code>: 还原所有按键绑定</li>
<li><code>key_listboundkeys</code>: 显示所有按键绑定</li>
<li><code>exec autoexec.cfg</code>: 在局内控制台使用, 可以自动使用更新后的cfg</li>
</ul>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">鼠标灵敏度</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">sensitivity</span> <span class="mf">1.20</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">zoom_sensitivity_ratio</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">按键绑定</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;z&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;slot10&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">火</span>                
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;c&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;slot8&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">烟</span>                   
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;v&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;slot3;slot7&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">闪</span>               
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;x&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;slot6&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">雷</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;q&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;slot11&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">电击枪</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;mouse5&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;+voicerecord&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">麦克风</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;capslock&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;+sprint&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">静步</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;shift&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;+duck&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">蹲</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;p&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;toggleconsole&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">控制台</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">unbind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;`&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">unbind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;u&#34;</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;ENTER&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;messagemode2&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">队内聊天</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">unbind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;y&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;</span><span class="se">\&#34;</span><span class="s2"> &#34;</span><span class="n">messagemode</span><span class="s2">&#34; // 全局聊天</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">alias</span> <span class="s2">&#34;fly_and_n&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team .fly; say_team .n&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;[&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;fly_and_n&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;]&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team .rethrow&#34;</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;,&#34;</span>  <span class="s2">&#34;+radialradio&#34;</span>  <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">快捷聊天轮盘</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;.&#34;</span>  <span class="s2">&#34;+radialradio2&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">快捷聊天轮盘</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;/&#34;</span>  <span class="s2">&#34;+radialradio3&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">快捷聊天轮盘</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">F1和F2要留给投票</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F3&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team .hp&#34;</span>      <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">血量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F4&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team .drop&#34;</span>    <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">发刀</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F5&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team .pause&#34;</span>   <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">暂停</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F6&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team .unpause&#34;</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">取消暂停</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F7&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team A!!!&#34;</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F8&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team B!!!&#34;</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">unbind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F9&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">unbind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F10&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F9&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team nice shot! 好枪! Хороший пистолет!&#34;</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;F10&#34;</span> <span class="s2">&#34;say_team nice try! 可惜! жаль! เสียดายมาก! ざんねん! 아쉽다! Tiếc quá!&#34;</span> 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">持枪视角</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">niko</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">viewmodel_fov</span> <span class="mi">68</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">viewmodel_offset_x</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">viewmodel_offset_y</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">viewmodel_offset_z</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.5</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">viewmodel_presetpos</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">donk</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">CSGO</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">NmcdV</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">ORLFj</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">vKC4W</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">LV6zW</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="n">fWjM</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">niko</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">CSGO</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">xQsAb</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">b7J42</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">qcvvS</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="n">AG9v</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">VwLXL</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">yekindar</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">CSGO</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">CBO9K</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">Nev5f</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">DkCEb</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">Hj7uY</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">OnMHA</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">我的准星</span><span class="p">:</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">CSGO</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">nB9k8</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">ebxVf</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">aKrMn</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">N2O27</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="n">MUnB</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">记得调准星厚度</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">准星</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">byzh</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshaircolor_r</span> <span class="mi">0</span>              <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">红色分量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshaircolor_g</span> <span class="mi">255</span>            <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">绿色分量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshaircolor_b</span> <span class="mi">213</span>            <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">蓝色分量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshair_drawoutline</span> <span class="mi">1</span>         <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">轮廓开关</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshair_outlinethickness</span> <span class="mf">0.2</span>  <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">轮廓厚度</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">准星</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">niko</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshaircolor_r</span> <span class="mi">0</span>              <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">红色分量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshaircolor_g</span> <span class="mi">255</span>            <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">绿色分量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshaircolor_b</span> <span class="mi">145</span>            <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">蓝色分量</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshair_drawoutline</span> <span class="mi">0</span>         <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">轮廓开关</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_crosshair_outlinethickness</span> <span class="mi">0</span>    <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">轮廓厚度</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairstyle</span> <span class="mi">4</span>              <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">静态准星</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshair_recoil</span> <span class="mi">0</span>            <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">跟随后坐力</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairdot</span> <span class="mi">0</span>                <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">取消中心点</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairsize</span> <span class="mi">1</span>               <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">长度</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairthickness</span> <span class="mi">1</span>          <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">粗细</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairgap</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">4</span>               <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">间隙</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairusealpha</span> <span class="mi">1</span>           <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">透明度开关</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairalpha</span> <span class="mi">255</span>            <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">透明度</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshair_t</span> <span class="mi">0</span>                 <span class="o">//</span> <span class="n">T形准星设置</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshairgap_useweaponvalue</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">准星间距设置</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span><span class="n">cl_crosshair_sniper_width</span> <span class="mi">1</span>      <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">狙击十字线粗细</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">投掷物准星</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshair_flash</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshairdelay_flash</span> <span class="mf">0.75</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshair_explosive</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshairdelay_explosive</span> <span class="mf">0.75</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshair_fire</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshairdelay_fire</span> <span class="mf">0.75</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshair_smoke</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshairdelay_smoke</span> <span class="mf">0.75</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshair_decoy</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_grenadecrosshairdelay_decoy</span> <span class="mf">0.75</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">雷达设置</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">bind</span> <span class="s2">&#34;`&#34;</span>  <span class="s2">&#34;toggleradarscale&#34;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cl_hud_radar_scale</span> <span class="mi">1</span>                <span class="o">//</span> <span class="err">雷达大小</span>
